               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">9th May 1865 ¶  ¶ I am instructed by the Honorable the Chief Secretary to inform you that it is necessary for all Departmental Bank accounts to be kept in future whenever practicable either at the ¶  ...</supplied>
