            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">65.05.09<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From John Moore</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">D1085, pp. 184-5, VPRS 1187/P outward correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">Trans 12.3.91. To proof</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                          style="font-weight: bold; background-color: #FFFF00; ">.</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                          style="font-weight: bold; background-color: #FFFF00; ">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Printed circular?</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>9th May 1865</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am instructed by the Honorable the Chief Secretary to inform you that it is necessary for all Departmental Bank accounts to be kept in future whenever practicable either at the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">national</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">RH: capital 'n'?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>or at the English Scottish and Australian Chartered Bank an arrangement having been agreed upon between the Government and these two institutions according to the terms of which the latter will allow interest on the weekly minimum balance standing to the departments credit in their books.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I enclose for your information a statement shewing the branches and agencies which the two banks have established within Victoria and request you will have the goodness to report the name and the address of any officer in your Department who in virtue of his office is in receipt of money for which it is desirable he shd keep an account at one of these - and the Bank Selected<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">RH: l.c. 's'?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am also to request that you will report the date on which you have commenced to carry into effect the instructions contained in this Circular with your own office account if it has not already been<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">dept</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">deposited?</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="2"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">Or kept?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>at either of the two Banks in question<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In M to J. McCulloch, 12 May 1865,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M reported<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>his<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Departmental banking arrangements.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">Sd J Moore</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanic Gardens</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; "
               xml:lang="en">Is this the enclosure from here on?If so should be noted</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
